{"tid":1819749,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"視點31 - 何君妖 vs 黃秋生","createTime":"2020-01-11T05:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T07:45:32.000Z","uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b49ad9ca019a0b6aea31a75916cdd8540894c8ef","tid":1819749,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/01/10/PBnI8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F10%2FPBnI8d.png&h=8d217dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台《視點31》去年11月邀請杜汶澤及陳百祥（阿叻）作嘉賓，被譽為「世紀之戰」。阿叻在節目中連番「我唔知」、「我睇唔到」、「我唔理」，阿澤事後直言與對方對話是「嘥x氣」。<br />\n<br />\n下周二14日，港台邀請到黃秋生和何君堯作《視點31》嘉賓，秋生表明是因為利君雅邀請，而非為何君堯而去，更明言<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果到時不是利君雅主持，他「一係走，一係坐喺度淨係飲茶唔講嘢。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據知港台最初想邀請秋生和施永青作嘉賓，但秋生坦言自己不熟經濟和地產，唔識討論黃色經濟圈問題，結果改為何君堯，以警暴為主題。秋生指何君堯高EQ，擅於利用情緒去達到想要的目的，他重申今次不是對決，只是兩個去接受利君雅訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/article/黃秋生VS何君堯！下周二「對戰」講警暴-oQ1wq6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Farticle%2F%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9FVS%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%EF%BC%81%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%B0%E3%80%8D%E8%AC%9B%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4-oQ1wq6&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjaDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=f5559a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/article/黃秋生VS何君堯！下周二「對戰」講警暴-oQ1wq6</a>"},{"pid":"bd5be2c19e2aebaa6778eeec60d9ab777628b2c7","tid":1819749,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"上次個主持實在太廢 , 俾叻狗搶晒啲 air time"},{"pid":"4cba5b7359aba3f72843d864ad61cc6917c98296","tid":1819749,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d6